	Applied naming convention changes:  Doc -> doc, Doc2 -> doc2.

	* src/lookat/lookat.cpp:  Changes associated with naming
	convention changes to doc, doc2.
	* src/openvrml/OpenVRML/doc.cpp:  Added file.  Replaces Doc.cpp,
