2002-10-26  Braden McDaniel  <braden@endoframe.com>

	Fixed crash when parsing IS mappings.

	* src/openvrml/OpenVRML/Vrml97Parser.cpp
	* src/openvrml/OpenVRML/Vrml97Parser.g
	* src/openvrml/OpenVRML/Vrml97Parser.hpp
